   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"Thonas and Kalalas to Dionysios, their father, greetings and well-being. I love you and daily I make mention of your excellent way of live to all the gods. Please, . . . come to us. Do everything possible to . . . us also . . .";(Verso): "From Kalalas and Thonas to Dionysios, their father."</ab>
         </div>
